msgstr "Domyślnie: 90 dni. Zalecane: 90–180."

#: includes/ccb-settings.php:351
msgid "After rejection (days)"
msgstr "Po odrzuceniu (dni)"

#: includes/ccb-settings.php:355
msgid ""
"Default: 1 day. Increase if you don't want to show the banner too often."
msgstr ""
"Domyślnie: 1 dzień. Zwiększ, jeśli nie chcesz wyświetlać baneru zbyt często."

#: includes/ccb-settings.php:362
